ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce de Notre-Dame-du-Lac CHANGE NAME / BOUNDARIES
PrecisApproval for the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE NOTRE-DAME-DU-LAC, in Quebec (a) to change its name to the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DU TÉMISCOUATA; and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to the municipalities of Saint-Honoré-de-Témiscouata, Saint-Louis-du-Ha! Ha!, Saint-Pierre-de-Lamy, Cabano, Saint-Elzéar-de-Témiscouata, Packington, Saint-Jean-de-la-Lande, Sainte-Rose-du-Dégelis, Saint-Juste-du-Lac, Lots-Renversés, Auclair, Lejeune, Saint-Michel-du-Squatec, Biencourt and Lac-des-Aigles.
